  <brief_title>HealthySteps: Exercise for Older Adults With Mobility Limitation</brief_title>
  <acronym>HealthySteps</acronym>
  <official_title>HealthySteps: A Pilot Randomized Controlled Trial of Exercise to Improve Walking Energetics, Fatigue, and Activity in Older Adults With Mobility Limitation</official_title>
